  "notes": "Hausa in Latin script (Boko). Implosives: Ɓ = /ɓ/, Ɗ = /ɗ/. Ƙ = ejective /kʼ/. Ts = ejective /tsʼ/. Ƴ = palatal glottal. 2-tone language (high, low) with falling contour. Long vowels written doubled.",
